originalText.text: Nice staff. Unfortunately, after going 4 times over the course of 4 months, my clothes have yet to smell clean. I think it's an issue with the dryers because they smell good coming out of the wash. I recently walked further to try a new laundromat and the difference was night and day. This place is so close to me so it's unfortunate I won't be going back.

originalText.text: This is a review for drop-off service. I started going here because they do a good job folding clothes and it's close to my house. Though, I still can't rave about them. They are the most expensive drop-off place I've ever been to and they want to be paid in cash when you are dropping off. Because of this, I just can't justify going here anymore. I shouldn't have to pay this much for drop-off.

originalText.text: This place is great for doing laundry.  The washers and dryers are newer, clean, and work well.  It is in an extremely small space, and you are often moving out of the way to let someone pass by.  Otherwise this place is awesome.
